title: Dating Yourself!

description:
In this episode, Kimberly Cobb talks about connecting with Brittany from "I Love A Mama's Boy" Season 3, shares her latest YouTube updates, shares 10 tips on how to date yourself, and more! 

 

Follow for weekly episodes of the "My Lips Aren't Sealed" podcast, where I discuss dating, fashion, entertainment, travel, pop culture, and more from my life! Thanks for listening!
